    <a href="#11-skysense-o-%e9%9d%a2%e5%90%91%e5%bc%80%e6%94%be%e4%b8%96%e7%95%8c%e9%81%a5%e6%84%9f%e8%a7%a3%e9%87%8a%e7%9a%84%e8%a7%86%e8%a7%89%e4%b8%ad%e5%bf%83%e8%a7%86%e8%a7%89%e8%af%ad%e8%a8%80%e5%bb%ba%e6%a8%a1" class="header-mark"></a>1.1 SkySense-O: 面向开放世界遥感解释的视觉中心视觉语言建模</h3><p><strong>论文标题</strong>: SkySense-O: Towards Open-World Remote Sensing Interpretation with Vision-Centric Visual-Language Modeling</p>
